identification division.
program-id. Test.

data division.
01 name picture is A(10).
01 summation picture is 9.
01 result picture is 9.

procedure division.
display "HELLO WORLD"
Display "Goedemorgen"
DISPLAY ""
display "12345"
DiSpLaY "NAME:" name
display "Enter value: " with no advancing

accept name

add 1 2 to summation

divide 1 into 2 giving result

multiply 2 by summation
multiply 3 by summation giving result
multiply 2 by summation result

move 5 to summation

evaluate 5
    when 1
        display "ONE"
    when other
        display "OTHER"
end

evaluate summation also result
    when 1 also 2
        display "BOTH MATCH"
end

perform task1
perform task1 through task2
perform task1 3 times
perform task1 through task2 5 times